WP Youtube Relevant Video Player embed relevant youtube video for your blog!

== Description ==

Automatically searches video from youtube relevant for your blog!
Also have option to display the youtube video of your choice just by copying the url!

== Installation ==

Upload the WP Youtube Relavant Video Player plugin to your blog, Activate it.
Give title. Enter url if you want your video to get embeded. Otherwise leave it blank for us to search you a relevant video.

1, 2, 3: You're done!

= 0.2 =
* Enables you to resize the video in three sizes.
